**Attack Scenario**:
```text
1. Attacker performs credential stuffing with 10,000 username/password combinations
2. No failed login attempts are logged
3. Attacker successfully compromises 47 accounts over 3 days
4. Organization has no record of the attack
5. Breach discovered 6 months later during unrelated audit
