**Additional Protections**:

- **Log shipping to immutable storage**: Send logs to append-only S3 bucket or write-once storage to prevent attacker log tampering
- **Real-time alerting integration**: Critical events (PRIVILEGE_ESCALATION, BRUTE_FORCE_DETECTED) trigger immediate alerts via PagerDuty/Slack
- **Log retention compliance**: 90-day retention for operational logs, 7-year retention for audit logs per SOX/PCI requirements
- **Sensitive data redaction**: Never log passwords, tokens, or PII in plain text; use tokenization or masking
- **Failed logging alerts**: Monitor for logging failures - if attackers disable logging, you need to know immediately

